node.text:
Zandvoort is back in F1 after a 36-year absence. What a track!!! Happy to drive you around there ahead of the Dutch GP. Some modifications on track since I raced here in F3 back in 2006/2007.
Full video on my YouTube channel.

ℹ️ Promo Code ZANDVOORT15 on Acer Stores. Link in bio.

#dutchF1 #zandvoort #romaingrosjean #predatorgaming #acer #orion5000 #xb3

F1 is back! Here is my track guide of Spa-Francorchamps.  Full explanation on my youtube channel. See you on @canalplus @canalplussport @la_f1_sur_canalplus 
 this weekend 📺

Sous-titres en Français. On se voit sur Canal + ce weekend. 

@predatorgaming 
 #belgiangp #predatorgaming #romaingrosjean #f1

node.text:
And now... It's Vlog time! 
9 exclusive minutes only for you! And some cool action on track for my first oval race ever. Enjoy! Merci. Link in bio. #indycar #bommarito500 #romaingrosjean

Now back to Europe for a bit before the last 3 @indycar races on the west coast
#thephoenix #stlouis #budweiser
